title: storybook-67-ch-6-par-1
transcription: Little Canary eats until he feels full. Then, he looks up …. Oh, where is his flock? How will he catch up? The song mother taught him! He must try to recall it.

title: storybook-73-ch-6-par-1
transcription: Will they play with me? I am so different from them.I should try.

title: storybook-74-ch-13-par-1

title: storybook-76-ch-6-par-1
